MultiTermAwareComponent
public class ICUTransformFilterFactory
extends TokenFilterFactory
implements MultiTermAwareComponent

Factory for ICUTransformFilter.

Supports the following attributes:

  • id (mandatory): A Transliterator ID, one from Transliterator.getAvailableIDs()
  • direction (optional): Either 'forward' or 'reverse'. Default is forward.
